imdb.plot outline: Goalstar is a docu-reality created and produced by ADD Agency for Hot Network. The program presents the activities of the football team composed of celebrities. Every episode, the team moves to another shared experience includes training and preparation for the games, the games themselves and the reactions afterwards.

plot: _Goalstar_ (qv) is a docu-reality created and produced by ADD Agency for Hot Network. The program presents the activities of the football team composed of celebrities. Every episode, the team moves to another shared experience includes training and preparation for the games, the games themselves and the reactions afterwards.::itay zalzman
